      "text": [
        "121 - وَ تَرَكَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ اَلسِّوَاكَ قَبْلَ أَنْ يُقْبَضَ بِسَنَتَيْنِ وَ ذَلِكَ أَنَّ أَسْنَانَهُ ضَعُفَتْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.121 - It is reported that Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) stopped using siwak two years before he passed away, as his teeth had weakened."
        ]
      }
    },
